  "instructions": [
    "Bring a large pot of salted water to a boil and cook the udon noodles according to the package instructions.",
    "Meanwhile, grill the binchotan charcoal until it is hot and smoking.",
    "In a large saucepan, combine the heavy cream, yuzu juice, and sake over medium heat.",
    "Whisk in the sour cream and sriracha sauce until smooth.",
    "Add the honey and whisk until dissolved.",
    "Season the broth with black pepper to taste.",
    "In a separate pan, melt the butter over medium heat.",
    "Add the shredded cheddar cheese and stir until melted and bubbly.",
    "To assemble the dish, place a portion of udon noodles on a plate or bowl.",
    "Ladle the hot broth over the noodles, followed by the cheese sauce.",
    "Slice the grilled turkey neck into thin strips and place on top of the noodles.",
    "Serve immediately and enjoy!"
